- Where does big data come from

* The sources are not generally new
  * The scale we use apply to it has changed
  * Sources in general
    * People
      * Soc media
    * Machines
      * Sensor
      * Industrial machinery or vehicles
    * Organisation
      * Databases structured or unstructured
  * Single Data sources by themselves are not that valuable as big data
    * Combining them has big data value
      * Wisdom
      * Knowledge
      * Information
    * Producing data enabled decisions and actions
    
    